EZ-Admin - Easy Linux System Administration Tool
================================================

EZ-Admin is a user-friendly, menu-driven tool for common Linux system
administration tasks.

USAGE:
------
Run with sudo privileges:
  sudo ez-admin

FEATURES:
---------
 0. Show help message
 1. Update System (apt update && upgrade)
 2. Cleanup (apt autoremove && clean)
 3. Install top 10 Tools (kali-linux-top10)
 4. Install cleaning Tool (BleachBit)
 5. Install git
 6. Install python3
 7. Make temporary SWAP RAM
 8. Install Ollama
 9. Install OpenWebUI
10. Run Clean Tool with pre-made settings
99. Exit

REQUIREMENTS:
-------------
- Linux system with APT package manager
- sudo/root privileges
- Internet connection for downloads

WARNING:
--------
This tool requires root privileges. Always review the source code
before running any tool with elevated permissions.

Source code available at: https://github.com/TherealONE12/EZ-Admin

